Sentencas: A model was developed for determining the current-temperature profiles of a solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process

Sentencas: The model was integrated by an electrochemical module and a thermal module.
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process

Sentencas: The electrochemical module included the three principal modes of polarization (i.e., ohmic, activation and concentration).
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process

Sentencas: The thermal module solved the energy and mass conservation equation using a unit cell approach.
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process

Sentencas: The integrated model (electrochemical-thermal) was used to analyze the performance of the cell with respect to different operating conditions.
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process

Sentencas: In addition, the model was used to analyze the response of the fuel cell under different gasifier compositions.
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process

Sentencas: These compositions are expected from the thermal integration of a downdraft gasifier with a solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process

Sentencas: The results showed the effect of the initial concentration of carbon monoxide, water and hydrogen, with respect to the performance of the cell.
Titulo: A cell-level model for a solid oxide fuel cell operated with syngas from a gasification process
